{{lead too short|date=November 2013}}
This following is a '''list of case colors and styles that have been produced for the [[Nintendo 3DS family]]''' of [[handheld game console]]s produced by [[Nintendo]]. Although the system initially launched with only two colors, its lineup has subsequently expanded to incorporate many more color varieties and limited editions, some of which are exclusive to various regions. As such, the list includes all color variations of regular [[Nintendo 3DS]] and [[New Nintendo 3DS]], as well as their larger models, the [[Nintendo 3DS XL]] and [[New Nintendo 3DS XL]] along with the Chinese version, the [[iQue#iQue 3DS XL|iQue 3DS XL]], and the entry-level versions, the [[Nintendo 2DS]] and [[New Nintendo 2DS XL]].

