===1960s=== ====1960–1964==== ''Shōnen Book'' finally launched into a new magazine. In addition to the launch, it now has several more series. Like many other manga magazines, it also adds series along the way. ''Shōnen Book'' grows with another set of series. Other manga pass and go. The past manga series end, a larger amount appears in the ''Shōnen Book'' magazine. The "God of Manga"; [[Osamu Tezuka]] gets hired to write and draw a manga for the ''Shōnen Book'' anthology, by the name of ''[[Shinsengumi]]''.
