amu no Bōken''|タムタムの冒険}} |January 1966 |June 1966 |Tarō Yamamoto × [[Shotaro Ishimori|Shōtarō Ishinomori]] |- |{{nihongo|''Kagaku Sen Sen, Taihei Yōsensō Monogatari''|科学戦戦・太平洋戦争物語}} |January 1963 |August 1963 |Yoshirō Akinaga × Shigeru Komatsuzaki |- |{{nihongo|''Nippon G7-Gō''|日本G7号}} |April 1966 |May 1967 |Saotto Makinichi × Fumiya Yoshida |- |{{nihongo|''Nirui Manrui''|二塁満塁}} |April 1966 |August 1966 |Hiroshi Sunada × Kei Wakana |- |{{nihongo|''Nikumarekko Monogatari''|にくまれっこ物語}} |July 1966 |December 1966 |Tarō Yamamoto × [[Shotaro Ishimori|Shōtarō Ishinomori]] |- |{{nihongo|''Dainiji Taisen''|第二次大戦}} |September 1966 |December 1966 |Tōboku Fujī × Shigeru Komatsuzaki |}
